# Run on production server (104.238.162.40):
#   cd /var/www/NPPC-Website && bash scripts/add_round13_nato3_milwaukee14_pratt.sh
#
# Source clusters:
#   - NATO 3 (May 2012 Chicago) — three out-of-state Occupy organizers
#     entrapped by Chicago Police undercover Officers Nadia Chikko and
#     Mehmet Uygur in advance of the May 20-21 NATO summit
#   - Geronimo ji Jaga Pratt — Black Panther leader and decorated Vietnam
#     combat veteran wrongly convicted 1972 in COINTELPRO frame-up;
#     conviction vacated 1997 after 27 years
#   - Milwaukee 14 (Sept 24, 1968) — Catholic Left raid on Milwaukee
